'''Mahmud Ibrahim Abunada''' ({{langx|ar|محمود إبراهيم أبو ندى}}; born 5 February 2000) is a Qatari professional [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Goalkeeper (association football)|goalkeeper]] for [[Qatari Stars League]] club [[Al-Rayyan SC|Al-Rayyan]] and the [[Qatar national football team|Qatar national team]].<ref name="mundial11">{{cite web|url=https://app.mundial11.com/players/5yw84ewmzo8ro79z|title=Mahmud Abunada|author=XS Studios|publisher=www.mundial11.ae|accessdate=2020-06-26}}</ref><ref>{{Soccerway|mahmud-ibrahim-abunad/591742|accessdate=26 June 2020}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.kooora.com/?player=154819|title=اللاعب : محمود إبراهيم أبو ندى|website=www.kooora.com|access-date=26 June 2020|archive-date=29 June 2023|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20230629085320/https://www.kooora.com/?player=154819|url-status=dead}}</ref>

==Career==
Abunada started his career at [[Al-Arabi SC (Qatar)|Al-Arabi]] and is a product of the Al-Arabi youth system. On 14 February 2019, he made his professional debut for Al-Arabi against [[Al-Rayyan SC|Al-Rayyan]] in the Pro League. By March 2020, he had appeared in 55 matches for the club.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://int.soccerway.com/matches/2019/02/14/qatar/stars-league/al-rayyan-sc/al-arabi-sc-doha-/2927921/|title=Al-Rayyan 3–1 Al-Arabi|website=Soccerway.com|publisher=Soccerway|accessdate=26 June 2020|date=14 February 2019}}</ref>

==International career==
Abunada was born in Qatar and is of Palestinian descent, holding dual Qatari and Palestinian citizenship. He plays for the [[Qatar national football team|Qatar national team]], and helped them earn qualification to the [[2026 FIFA World Cup]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.cairo24.com/2301110|title=محمود أبو ندى.. من شوارع غزة إلى المونديال بقميص قطر|date=17 October 2025|website=القاهرة 24}}</ref>

==Personal life==
After qualifying to the [[2026 FIFA World Cup]], Abunada donated to build a hospital in the [[Gaza Strip]] in Palestine to help them recover from the [[Gaza war]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.alaraby.co.uk/sport/%D8%BA%D8%B2%D8%A9-%D9%81%D9%8A-%D9%82%D9%84%D8%A8-%D9%86%D8%AC%D8%A7%D8%AD%D8%A7%D8%AA-%D9%82%D8%B7%D8%B1-%D9%88%D8%AD%D8%A7%D8%B1%D8%B3-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%B9%D9%86%D8%A7%D8%A8%D9%8A-%D9%8A%D8%B3%D9%8A%D8%B1-%D8%B9%D9%84%D9%89-%D8%AE%D8%B7%D9%89-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%87%D9%8A%D8%AF%D9%88%D8%B3?amp|title=غزة في قلب نجاحات قطر وحارس العنابي يسير على خطى الهيدوس}}</ref>

